		"description": "Base URL: `http://127.0.0.1:8000/`\n\n## üîê Authentication\n\n- **Token Type**: Bearer Token\n    \n- **How to Get**: Use the `/login` endpoint to retrieve `access_token`.\n    \n\n---\n\n## 1\\. üìù Sign Up\n\n**Endpoint:** `POST /signup`  \n**Auth:** ‚ùå Not required  \n**Body (JSON):**\n\n```\n{\n  \"email\": \"example@mail.com\",\n  \"password\": \"yourpassword\",\n  \"role\": \"ops\"  // or \"client\"\n}\n\n ```\n\n**Response:** Returns user creation confirmation or error.\n\n---\n\n## 2\\. üîë Log In\n\n**Endpoint:** `POST /login`  \n**Auth:** ‚ùå Not required  \n**Body (JSON):**\n\n```\n{\n  \"email\": \"example@mail.com\",\n  \"password\": \"yourpassword\"\n}\n\n ```\n\n**Response:**\n\n```\n{\n  \"access_token\": \"your-jwt-token\"\n}\n\n ```\n\nUse this token in subsequent requests as `Bearer Token`.\n\n---\n\n## 3\\. üì§ Upload File\n\n**Endpoint:** `POST /upload`  \n**Auth:** ‚úÖ Required  \n**Form-Data:**\n\n- `file`: Upload `.pptx`, `.docx`, or `.xlsx` file only\n    \n\n**Response:** Confirmation message or validation error.\n\n---\n\n## 4\\. üìÉ List Files\n\n**Endpoint:** `GET /list_files`  \n**Auth:** ‚úÖ Required  \n**Response:** List of available files for the authenticated user.\n\n---\n\n## 5\\. üîó Request Secure Download Link\n\n**Endpoint:** `GET /download/{filename}`  \n**Auth:** ‚úÖ Required  \n**Example:**  \n`GET /download/data-1749407797375.xlsx`\n\n**Response:**\n\n```\n{\n  \"message\": \"success\",\n  \"download-link\": \"http://127.0.0.1:8000/download_secure/<token>\"\n}\n\n ```\n\nThe link is encrypted and time-limited.\n\n---\n\n## 6\\. ‚¨áÔ∏è Secure File Download\n\n**Endpoint:** `GET /download_secure/{token}`  \n**Auth:** ‚úÖ Required  \n**Description:** Downloads the file securely using encrypted URL.\n\n---\n\n## üåê Environment Variables Used in Postman\n\n- `{{access_token}}`: Set after login\n    \n- `{{secure_encrypted_token}}`: Set after download link request\n    \n\nEndFragment",
